text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This obsoletes IRM 3.34.4, National Research Program, S Corporation Tax Returns - Document Analysis & Data Entry

The material in IRM section 3.34.4 is obsolete because the study referenced is complete and the processes are not active for current NRP operations. If needed, prior guidance information can be found in the IRS repository. Go to http://oldirm.web.irs.gov/ for more information.
IRM 3.34.4, dated 12-01-2006 is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal.
